visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: handwriting
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Norican

designer: Vernon Adams

approved: true
description: <p>Norican is a script-like display font \
  designed to be used freely across the internet by web \
  browsers on desktop computers, laptops and mobile \
  devices. Norican's design is based on the merging of \
  a number of old script fonts, most notably Stephenson \
  Blake's 'Glenmoy' from the 1920s.</p>

font.Norican-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Norican-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

